本的二十分之一。这能否帮助 OpenAI 赢得开发者的心呢？飙升 4500%！OpenAI 年化收入达 13 亿美元，11 月或迎重磅升级 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2c1026ab56d7aa6c94ac52bd4e7e71e3_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "124 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626112796"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/8zs3MPQkfMrEAMaCTEwMTQxNTI4MSDuuampBjAAOGBABXIJNjI2MTEyNzk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1697299720.761031", "card_id": "Q_624214923", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "马拉松跑者在跑到 35 公里后在想什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "跑过若干场马拉松，在后半程那个思绪，那个埋怨，那个颓废，难以言状。请问大家那时都在想什么？怎么看待这群无畏又无助的人？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-103efe0e34487a8fc3f07e026b1e6aef_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624214923"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/8zs3MPQkfMrEAMaCTEwMDk5MzYxMSCd99WoBjAAODhABnIJNjI0MjE0OTIzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1697299720.761448", "card_id": "Q_625936518", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 IVE 回归主打曲《Baddie》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7